BA Advert 27-02-2023
The ideal candidate is a team player who will be responsible for working with company data in various business areas. Specific responsibilities include reporting metrics, analyzing methodologies, suggesting operation improvements, and building proposal evaluations in a cross-functional environment. 

Responsibilities

Participate Business Analysis of Pre-Sales requirements 
Build cross-functional partnerships, internally and externally
Manage Stakeholders
Maintain a competitive market knowledge
Work closely with the Architects on High Level Designs
Write Proposals


Qualifications

Bachelor's degree or equivalent experience
At least 6 years expereince on Business Analysis
Fluency in Microsoft Office suite (Outlook, Excel, Word, PowerPoint, etc.)
Strong written, verbal and collaboration skills
BCS BA Certification
Must have previous working experience with the UK Government as BA
Experience Facilitating workshops
Excellent understanding of Agile Techniques
Exposure to all cycles of development
Familiar with Togaf
Experience with Facing Customer and Internal Stakeholders
